The paper deals with Distributed Constraint Optimization Problems (DCOPs) and proposes a method to accelerate belief propagation algorithms. This falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the theoretical analysis of the proposed method, which falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). The method involves optimizing the search space, which is related to Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper deals with optimization and control, which falls under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
